      <title>杠杆贷款是信贷市场警告的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-25/leveraged-loans-are-focus-of-warnings-in-credit-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的奥利维亚·雷蒙德报道称，随着美联储长期较高利率的做法引发了人们对高收益债券市场降级和违约风险的担忧，杠杆贷款及其可变利率成为焦点。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-25/leveraged-loans-are-focus-of-warnings-in-credit-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 17:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
